      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_02-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "木の板はこれくらいで足りるかな～？\n電動ドライバーとネジも必要だよね",
      "startTime": 6.5666666309,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_02-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "あとはペンキと刷毛と木工用ボンドと……",
      "startTime": 9.7333352048,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
